I had an extremely disappointing experience with this store. I ordered a sleeveless top in size M, which was incredibly expensive, only to receive a product so short that it barely reached my waist. When I contacted customer service, they suggested an exchange instead of a refund. Following their instructions, I returned the item at my own expense. However, as the package was about to reach them, I discovered that they were no longer at the provided location, and they ignored my emails for over a week.

After a long delay, they finally responded, but by then, the package had been returned to me. At this point, I had lost all trust in them, and my money was essentially wasted. Their lack of professionalism and poor communication make it impossible for me to recommend this store to anyone.

review_title: Expensive, Poorly Sized Product & Awful Customer Service
review_content:
I had an extremely disappointing experience with this store. I ordered a sleeveless top in size M, which was incredibly expensive, only to receive a product so short that it barely reached my waist. When I contacted customer service, they suggested an exchange instead of a refund. Following their instructions, I returned the item at my own expense. However, as the package was about to reach them, I discovered that they were no longer at the provided location, and they ignored my emails for over a week.

After a long delay, they finally responded, but by then, the package had been returned to me. At this point, I had lost all trust in them, and my money was essentially wasted. Their lack of professionalism and poor communication make it impossible for me to recommend this store to anyone.
